{\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having learned his lessons from a disappointing campaign in the previous Tokyo Games, the 24-year-old star fueled medal hopes as he placed second in floor exercise and sixth in vault - events where he won world titles.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his lessons\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointing campaign\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"the 24-year-old star\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"medal hopes\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"floor exercise\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"vault - events\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"world titles\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo also did fairly well in the four other apparatuses, totaling 83.631 points to reach the all-around finals at ninth place.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yulo\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the four other apparatuses\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"83.631 points\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around finals\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"ninth place\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top 24 in the all-around and the top eight in each apparatus advanced to the finals.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the all-around\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"each apparatus\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bearing the responsibility of winning the Philippines' first Olympic gymnastics medal, Yulo showed he has what it takes as he shone in his pet events, recording 14.766 points in floor exercise and averaging 14.683 points in vault.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.6678934824456046, \"rank\": 0.49721000107928814, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the responsibility\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"Yulo\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"his pet events\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"14.766 points\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"floor exercise\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"14.683 points\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Great Britain's Jake Jarman netted a higher score than Yulo in the floor exercise qualification with 14.966 points, while defending champion Artem Dolgopyat of Israel landed at seventh with 14.466 points.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6049836084086225, \"rank\": 0.6478056636216873, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 0.9937816377359641, \"rank\": 0.0034186218768425206, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 1490, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9324185041444905, \"rank\": 0.07247958624116037, \"text\": \"